title: Snaps -Scott Frost fired from Nebraska, Notre Dame loses QB, Texas A&M done? + Aaron's top 5 QBs
itunes:title: Snaps -Scott Frost fired from Nebraska, Notre Dame loses QB, Texas A&M done? + Aaron's top 5 QBs
description:
T-Bob Hebert and Aaron Murray react to Scott Frost being fired from Nebraska, Notre Dame's starting quarterback Tyler Buchner's season-ending injury, and Texas A&M's shocking loss to Appalachian State. Later, Aaron Murray shares his top 5 quarterbacks from Week 2 including Texas' Quinn Ewers, Arkansas' KJ Jefferson, USC's Caleb Williams, Mississippi State's Will Rogers, and Wake Forest's Sam Hartman. #volume #herd #colincowherd
